Samuel Lewis said his mother had warned John that “don't get in trouble, do not get into trouble.”
He added that John did not heed the mother's warning, saying: “We all know John always gets into trouble, always getting into trouble, but that's because it's a good trouble because it is sticking to the right thing.”
