Chinanews.com, Chongqing, July 26 (Reporter Han Lu) The reporter learned from the China Railway Chengdu Bureau Group Co., Ltd. on the 26th that the Zheng Wan High Speed Rail Small Three Gorges Tunnel, which is about 18.9 km long, passed through the same day.
It is understood that the Small Three Gorges Tunnel is not only the longest high-speed rail tunnel in the area of the Three Gorges reservoir area, but also is currently under construction project, design the longest single-hole two-line high-speed rail tunnel with a speed of 350 km/h.
Zheng Wan high-speed rail is located in the territory of three provinces in Henan, Hubei and Chongqing, in Zhengzhou north of Beijing-Guang, Xulan high-speed rail, in Wanzhou South Lian Yuwan high-speed rail arrived in Chongqing, is an important part of China's “eight vertical and eight horizontal” high-speed railway network along the river channel and Hunan channel.
Zheng Wan high-speed rail small three gorges tunnel on the 26th through the whole line.
Figure shows through the site.
Zheng Wan high-speed rail from Zhengzhou City, Henan Province, to the southwest via Pingdingshan, Nanyang City, Xiangyang City, Hubei Province to Wanzhou District of Chongqing. The new line is about 818 km long, the design speed 350 km/h, the territory of Chongqing is about 184 km.
Among them, the Zhengzhou-Xiangyang section has been pre-opened on December 1, 2019, and the Chongqing section is stepping up construction.
On the 26th, the small three gorges tunnel is Zheng Wan high-speed rail full control project, the project is located at the junction of Fengjie County of Chongqing and Wushan County, the length of about 18.9 km, the maximum depth of 890 meters.
Construction of the tunnel began in February 2017 and was fully integrated on 26 July 2020.
According to Wang Guojun, head of the tunnel design director of China Railway Eryuan Engineering Group Co., Ltd. of China Railway Eryuan Engineering Group Co., Ltd., according to Wang Guojun, the location of the small Three Gorges tunnel is very complex, facing karst, mud water and large deformation of soft rock. It is a class I high-risk tunnel, tunnel design and construction difficult. Degree is great.
“In the process of construction, we used geological survey, geophysical and advance drilling methods to advance geological prediction, and have adopted special designs for more than 30 types of caverns. “For example, 24 meters long bridges are designed to avoid tunnel settlement across large caverns with a longitudinal length of over 10 meters and depths of over 55 meters in the tunnel.” Wang Guojun said.
According to the construction party of China Railway Tunnel Bureau, the tunnel was constructed using a combination of grooming blocking. By constructing cross-cavern leveling guide, grouting water blocking, strengthening tunnel structural support, and building sewage treatment stations, both ensured the orderly progress of the project and avoided construction drainage damage to the water body in the small Three Gorges scenic area. When successfully overcome the 7 km long soft rock deformation and other bad geology, the maximum daily water inflow of 157,000 Cubic meters of multi-mud water and other construction problems.
After the completion of the whole line of the Zheng Wan high-speed rail, it will become the new convenient and fast passenger transport main channel in southwest China to Central Plains, North China and Northeast China, to improve the capacity and quality of the northeast railway corridor in southwest China, improve the regional network layout, accelerate the development of tourism resources along the route and urbanization process, promote regional It is of great importance to coordinate development and promote the implementation of the Western Development Strategy.
